<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="limit-n">limit <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɪmɪt/    美 /'lɪmɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>界限；边界：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>in the <strong>city limits</strong> 
在市区内</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>within a twenty-mile limit 
20英里范围内</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>限度；限制：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>time / speed limit</strong>
时间/速度限制</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Even below the drinking limit, driving will be affected.
即使是低于饮酒限度，开车也会受到影响。</p><footer>2011 福建</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>极限：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He tried my patience to its limits. 
他把我的耐心逼到了极限。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The limits of a person's intelligence are fixed at birth, but whether he reaches these limits will depend on his environment.
一个人的智力极限是生来就确定了的，但是否能达到这些极限取决于他所处的环境。</p><footer>2012 安徽</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="within-limits">within limits</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在某种范围内；适度地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm willing to help, within limits.
我愿意帮忙，可是有一定限度。</p></div></div>